  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b89\u0ba3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bc1 : \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc7 \u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b9c\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka situation is sensitive: India's focus on helping - Jaishankar",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "Indian External Affairs Minister S Jaishankar has said that the situation in Sri Lanka is very sensitive.",
        "He mentioned this in a press conference in Kerala and said that the situation in Sri Lanka is very sensitive and confusing and the situation has changed even as we are talking here.",
        "\"We are committed to helping the Sri Lankan people as they are our neighbours, they are very friendly people and we want to help them because they are in a very difficult situation and we have been very supportive of that country for the past few months,\" he said.",
        "Our focus is on Sri Lanka's economic situation and how we can help. We are not involved in other issues, we are only focused on economic issues, we are not concerned about other issues, and we cannot respond to everything that is published on social media."
      ],
